product_entries.section_context_for_this_product_block: ELECTRICAL WORKS > PLUGS, SOCKETS AND JUNCTION BOXES
product_entries.full_product_description: Termination of XLPE insulated armoured power cables (up to 1100 V grade) and connection of leads excluding the supply of cable glands and lugs but including fixing of cable glands, supply and fixing of PVC shrouds for outdoor terminations, cutting and stripping of cable insulation, crimping the lug on to the conductor, clamping of the cable-cores, marking with wire number, ferrules etc., including all labour and materials, as per approved drawings, specifications of this tender and directions of Engineer-in-Charge. Cables with OD upto 20 mm.
